@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave
@employeeId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002

# Setelah Direct Create berhasil, copy ID dari response lalu paste di sini
@requestId = 5cd49a29-60c6-4a09-afee-440fd64235ef


### ======================================================
### 1. SERVICE CHECK
### ======================================================

### Service Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/


### Metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/$metadata


### ======================================================
### 2. READ DATA
### ======================================================

### Get All Leave Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests


### Get Active Leave Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests?$filter=IsActiveEntity eq true


### Get Leave Requests with Approval History
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests?$expand=LeaveApprovals


### ======================================================
### 3. DIRECT CREATE ACTIVE
### ======================================================
### Requires package.json:
### "cds": {
###   "fiori": {
###     "direct_crud": true
###   }
### }

### Direct Create Active Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic employee@company.com:123456

{
  "Reason": "Annual leave using direct create active flow",
  "Employee_ID": "{{employeeId}}",
  "Status": "Drafted",
  "RequestDate": "2026-05-05T09:00:00Z"
}


### ======================================================
### 4. READ CREATED ACTIVE DATA
### ======================================================
### Paste ID from Direct Create response into @requestId first

### Read Active Leave Request by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{requestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)


### ======================================================
### 5. SUBMIT ACTIVE LEAVE REQUEST
### ======================================================

### Submit Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{requestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.submit
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### Read Submitted Leave Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{requestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)


### ======================================================
### 6. APPROVE SUBMITTED LEAVE REQUEST
### ======================================================

### Approve Leave Request
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave/LeaveRequests(ID='{{requestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.approve
Authorization: Basic manager@company.com:123456
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Comments": "Approved using real approve-leave.js"
}


### Read Approved Leave Request with History
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{requestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals